GrubTurbo fixes the problem by presenting the user with a number of restaurants around a X mile radius. The app will use a swiping mechanism similar to that of Tinder, in which the user will swipe left to remove/dislike and right to select/like. 
After selecting the one that they like, the user will have the option to set the restaurant as the destination in google maps.
